snippet.title: Dark Table CCG - Alpha Teaser Trailer
snippet.description:
Dark Table CCG is coming to Closed Alpha Q1 of 2023. Preorder your Skeleton Key now and unlock all cards at a reduced price, as well as exclusive items for backers.

Preorder and read more on the game mechanics at https://darktableccg.com

Join our Discord server and chat with us at: https://discord.gg/pczabgh
